data.description: A Unique Find! Over 4,000 sq feet 5 bedrooms retreat nestled in a serene oasis on a quiet cul-de-sac. Extensively remodeled & reimagined by the current owner/designer to include the perfect balance between nature & modern luxury. 14'+ vaulted cedar ceilings in the social areas surrounded by impact glass walls, a gourmet state-of-the-art kitchen w/2 long cooking islands encasing a multitude of gas & electric premiere appliance that will impress the most discerning chef. 2 generously sized en suite bedrooms: 1 primary & a 2nd for extended family. All bedrooms are sanctuaries of relaxation & the baths of showroom style.A tropical patio/pool/summer kitchen area is enormous. Hidden features: 500 gal propane tank, EV charging station, gas hook-up for future generator, & boat/RV canopy. MUST SEE!
